# Production build environment for the Clear Skies dashboard.
#
# VITE_SSE_URL — same-origin path to the live Server-Sent Events stream.
# Caddy reverse-proxies /sse to the realtime service (port 8766) on the same
# origin as the dashboard, so a relative path is correct here. This MUST be
# set at build time; if it is empty, getSseUrl() returns "" and the dashboard
# silently runs REST-only with no live (MQTT) updates.
VITE_SSE_URL=/sse
